      "para_id": "Q004973.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) Ibbi-Suen , the god of his land , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters , presented this ( seal ) to Lu-Šu-Suenka , the envoy , child of Lugal-durgare , the envoy , his servant ."
    }
  ],
